       personal assistant.
     * [https://lightberry.eu/]Lightberry - Led lighting solution
       dedicated for raspberry pi and your TV.
     * [https://github.com/SecPi/SecPi]SecPi - Raspberry Pi based home
       alarm system.
     * [https://github.com/n0bel/PiClock]PiClock - Fancy Clock built
       around a monitor and a Raspberry Pi.
     * [https://github.com/benjefferies/gogo-garage-opener]Garage Door
