     * [https://github.com/stevelacy/movel]Movel - Raspberry Pi car
       computer.
     * [https://github.com/winkidney/PIFanTuner]PiFanTuner - CPU-fan-tuner
       daemon, just enables your fan as necessary.
       Supports Raspberry Pi 3
     * [https://samy.pl/skyjack/]SkyJack - Take over and allow full
       control over any Parrot AR Drone within wireless distance.
     * [https://github.com/nerves-project]Nerves Project - Craft and
       deploy bulletproof embedded software in Elixir.
     * [https://github.com/rothgar/rpi-wordpress]Wordpress using Docker -
       Run a Wordpress site in containers with dynamic DNS.
